{"tid":1290692,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"連自己感受都照顧唔到 仲要照顧女友感受","createTime":"2019-07-06T14:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T16:38:32.000Z","uid":156327,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c564d11c0dd8c37dc8830ff389734369ae80199","tid":1290692,"uid":156327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"所以 拍拖 不了<br />\n利申 抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e2f781007711e9e1ea4ef440d92ca4349a50d3","tid":1290692,"uid":156327,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"自己負自己<br />\n<br />\n早瞓都有壓力 令自己瞓唔著<br />\n食藥太多又唔醒<br />\n食太少又無效<br />\n九點半食左藥到而家<br />\n聽日仲要早起身"},{"pid":"42e9f4a52dce23457798d9927f126ee908115cbf","tid":1290692,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:52:26.000Z","msg":"互相照顧"},{"pid":"92ddd58051dd894ab3b0be353449c3eaa0f7aad7","tid":1290692,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"曾經做過金融才俊<br />\n讚美聲中患上抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔敢諗衰左個陣 家人朋友會點對我<br />\n唔係我份人唔好 只係個社會見高拜見低踩"},{"pid":"818d0c37abfcc06e0d1d4689d8d0a24feb1ac2ce","tid":1290692,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"兩次自殺紀錄 最近個次係上星期<br />\n努力工作 集中精神 遠離負面情緒<br />\n點知仲比左壓力自己 強迫自己好返"},{"pid":"12c20f336edf383421f540280cd66c6ae58a7205","tid":1290692,"uid":213770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:38:53.000Z","msg":"手足 一步一步慢慢嚟啦<br />\n事情會變好架"},{"pid":"2b99731f161bc04c698e6abff1bd8dbe965afbb9","tid":1290692,"uid":215706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:53:47.000Z","msg":"又差啲以為自己開post... <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701cbd60cc81f56a6ca1656fe5aa7712f3be30af","tid":1290692,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"818d0c37abfcc06e0d1d4689d8d0a24feb1ac2ce","tid":1290692,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"兩次自殺紀錄 最近個次係上星期<br />\n努力工作 集中精神 遠離負面情緒<br />\n點知仲比左壓力自己 強迫自己好返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zedFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=c7a7d8c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zedFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=4d17362d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"2ee1e43c6b2e88a2a0331de6bb134bb060385f3e","tid":1290692,"uid":35888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但同人冇Connection 又會加劇病情<br />\n好似一個冇得醫嘅循環咁"},{"pid":"a82da4598d3e4ffdd161c6431ff8723ed3cdaa60","tid":1290692,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ee1e43c6b2e88a2a0331de6bb134bb060385f3e","tid":1290692,"uid":35888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"